, si 
\begin_inset Formula $G\leq_{A}F$
\end_inset

 con 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 libre, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

 es libre y 
\begin_inset Formula $\text{rg}G\leq\text{rg}F$
\end_inset

.
 
